{"original_text": "#早课# 妙法莲华经（片段）。 照片剪裁之前后对照之。", "evtlist": [607], "uid": "1263406744", "dep": 0, "text": "#早课# 妙法莲华经（片段）。 照片剪裁之前后对照之。", "pid": "", "tr": 6, "mid": "3866649813439389", "times": 1, "childnum": 6, "t": 1437364617, "totalChildren": 6, "dr": 6, "children": [{"evtlist": [607], "uid": "1225279591", "dep": 0, "text": "@司马南 你心情不好吗？——你这字，嗨，怎么越发疲软了呢？[酷]", "pid": "3866649813439389", "tr": 0, "mid": "3866650346893614", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1437364744, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "王祖哲"}, {"evtlist": [607], "uid": "1151924885", "dep": 0, "text": "抄点马列多好啊！什么佛经，尽是狗屁！", "pid": "3866649813439389", "tr": 0, "mid": "3866652372853982", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1437365227, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "帅子325"}, {"evtlist": [607], "uid": "3515238672", "dep": 0, "text": "司马的这种坚持与自律不是一般人能做到的，我就是抽烟上比较能坚持。", "pid": "3866649813439389", "tr": 0, "mid": "3866652414527889", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1437365237, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "贾话筒"}, {"evtlist": [607], "uid": "2872521342", "dep": 0, "text": "司马大哥写点楷体，让兄弟描描。", "pid": "3866649813439389", "tr": 0, "mid": "3866672261573742", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1437369968, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "恒岳他爸"}, {"evtlist": [607], "uid": "1458492717", "dep": 0, "text": "人既可褒贬，字亦有千秋。司马先生的小楷书法已然功力不凡。书道人伦，理应相生相长。", "pid": "3866649813439389", "tr": 0, "mid": "3866677894763960", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1437371312, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "长乐乡人"}, {"evtlist": [607], "uid": "2325082392", "dep": 0, "text": "【名家欣赏】读经书，静下心!", "pid": "3866649813439389", "tr": 0, "mid": "3866804743565614", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1437401555, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "一灵致远"}], "name": "司马南"}